FT  04 AUG 94 / Beta Global net asset value at 172.5p
Beta Global Emerging Markets Investment Trust had a net asset value of
172.5p per share at June 30, a fall of 18 per cent since end-December.
On a year-on-year basis, however, the value showed an increase of 31 per
cent.
Losses after tax widened to Pounds 623,000 (Pounds 97,000) during the six
months, for losses of 0.2p (0.3p) per share.
